Fish App API Documents

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1 - Signup API

http://7586a6d7.ngrok.io/adduser

{
    "adduserdata" : {
        "email": "d@gmail.com",
        "full_name": "Deepak",
        "mob_code": "",
        "mob_number": "",
        "password1" : 12345678,
        "platform": "IOS"
    }
}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2 - Email Code Verification

http://7586a6d7.ngrok.io/forgotpassword

{
    "forgotpassword":{
        "email":"rsengar7@gmail.com",
        "platform": "IOS"
    }
}
