7 - Logout 

http://7d5d48e7.ngrok.io/logout

{
    "logout": {
        "userid":1
    }
}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
8 - Update Profile

http://7d5d48e7.ngrok.io/userprofile

{
    "userprofile": {
        "userid":"asd1@gmail.com",
        "profilepic":"",
